# Code owners for review routing (.specs/04-canonical-vs-community.md).
# OWNERS files inside packs are maintenance routing; this file drives the
# required-review gate.

# Design, tooling, governance, and the skill set: atheory-ai maintainers.
/.specs/                       @atheory-ai/skillex-maintainers
/scripts/                      @atheory-ai/skillex-maintainers
/.github/                      @atheory-ai/skillex-maintainers
/skills/                       @atheory-ai/skillex-maintainers
/registry/                     @atheory-ai/skillex-maintainers
/LICENSE                       @atheory-ai/skillex-maintainers
/NOTICE                        @atheory-ai/skillex-maintainers
/DCO                           @atheory-ai/skillex-maintainers
/CONTRIBUTING.md               @atheory-ai/skillex-maintainers

# Canonical packs: maintainer review required (2 approvals via branch
# protection; see .github/BRANCH_PROTECTION.md).
/ecosystems/*/packs/atheory-ai/   @atheory-ai/skillex-maintainers

# Community packs: on acceptance, add a line routing the handle's directory
# to that handle's owners so they can self-approve subsequent revisions, e.g.
#   /ecosystems/javascript/packs/alice/   @alice
#   /ecosystems/javascript/packs/acme-labs/   @acme-labs/maintainers
